  "id": "perf-ladder-large",
  "purpose": "Perf-ladder rung 3 (large): 1000 nodes / 6000 edges, a 4-deep rule chain (seed->t1->t2->t3->t4) plus a 4-clause triangle join rule (t5(x) <- t1(y), rel0(x,y), rel1(y,z), rel2(x,z) \u2014 the hello-world join shape at scale, the grounding stressor), 60 staggered-window seed facts, timesteps=75 \u2014 explicitly bounded per the ladder's B16 constraint (docs/perf/ladder.md). Default engine config; the t4 and t5 frames pin the chain's deep end and the join, get_time pins the loop length. Laptop-local by design: sized by the committed screens in docs/perf/ladder.md.",
